{"tid":690672,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[烙印掘起]傳中國強制要求LG Display轉讓OLED技術","createTime":"2018-06-05T05:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T16:22:13.000Z","uid":47132,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2c20ce1ced02623c622c4d1e45877834ea5697","tid":690672,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:13:31.000Z","msg":"南韓傳媒引述消息報道，中國政府要求LG Display轉讓OLED生產技術，以換取批准其在中國廣州建廠。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，消息指中國亦要求LG Display於中國建設OLED研發中心，並在當地採購零件及耗材。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，LG Display計劃不遲於2019年下半年在廣州建設OLED面板工廠，並早已於2017年8月開始施工。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，外電報道，全球最大的兩家晶片製造商三星電子及SK海力士半導體表示，正在接受中國監管機構的調查。美光科技此前亦接受了類似的調查。"},{"pid":"065d04bcc88687458902bfaa60929ce9db1bd473","tid":690672,"uid":11962,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"哇，夾硬搶"},{"pid":"ed26e0e4b51702f20a34ffc8d83b64ccb9ab021c","tid":690672,"uid":8040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"去越南開廠咪無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e6ff313d9c86865879b570152bc2acb698cce8","tid":690672,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065d04bcc88687458902bfaa60929ce9db1bd473","tid":690672,"uid":11962,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"哇，夾硬搶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"係好過搶"},{"pid":"650fb9ab7208041efe1626bd1e0e6495699bcc24","tid":690672,"uid":33061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩利害我的國"},{"pid":"8e22a31531ca55f774e7f9939861bfe8b3347635","tid":690672,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:31:34.000Z","msg":"一拍兩散，炒哂啲工人，去第二度開"},{"pid":"9d533a0a03afd9515fbd6ccf3fe764a6cf9f48ad","tid":690672,"uid":188849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:38:28.000Z",